item.title: CVE-2021-25002|2024-08-03T19:49:14.548Z -- unknown -- tipsacarrier
item.description: The Tipsacarrier WordPress plugin before 1.5.0.5 does not have any authorisation check in place some functions, which could allow unauthenticated users to access Orders data which could be used to retrieve the client full address, name and phone via tracking URL
